{"tid":1604080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！唔撚想十月一仲係咁","createTime":"2019-09-30T00:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:53:13.000Z","uid":290364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4250198917cb8e4af22dcb4b5dc1baa5970d2e19","tid":1604080,"uid":290364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:43:56.000Z","msg":"大家要記住 ！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當你擰轉頭就跑既時候 前邊已經有無數手足比人禁低左</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係意識問題 大家出得去就係一條心 當每個手足係家人 <br />\n唔好返到屋企就對住d片係到打飛機 每人做多少少得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">擰轉頭就跑，手足比狗咬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2ece626ffb0585acb0e99cec95f7c3e2595c54","tid":1604080,"uid":290364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af3b5f396ee093992703dc01b46c85cacc899a4","tid":1604080,"uid":290364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc11f65e81e92cb2575b289267be7513ea5b0b0","tid":1604080,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:08:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f604af50dad37f7a5cb6ebc456d833755a2592f2","tid":1604080,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"仲有講撚左好多次,萬一比狗捉撚住個書包,第一件事要好似火影跑咁鬆開個書包走左先<br />\n<br />\n當然啦,最好就書包向前啦,但有時阻住行動都無計<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要火影跑,唔好本能反能chok 手跑"},{"pid":"d05122ac8edf925051f16e58e6960e784df125a3","tid":1604080,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前嚟講火魔法係最撚勁嘅野<br />\n但永遠都好似唔夠多咁<br />\n如果和理非可以幫手帶火魔法材料會唔會幫倒好撚大忙<br />\n每人跟生日日期帶其中一樣 <br />\n俾狗check袋都唔知入你乜撚野<br />\n例如1-5號帶玻璃樽（岩岩飲完未扔）<br />\n6-10號帶砂糖<br />\n11-20號白電油/汽油（入火機食煙、露營用，五金鋪買）<br />\n20-25號打火機（食煙）<br />\n26-30號帶毛巾仔<br />\n唔知齊未 見酒精都得帶出去風險好似仲低啲<br />\n不過易tk<br />\n到時收集完再傳俾前線<br />\n其他物資照舊<br />\n可以分散風險<br />\n不過唔知係咪大部分前線都會玩火魔法<br />\n前線可唔可以話俾大家聽可以點幫 帶啲咩 做咩好<br />\n<br />\n或者一人一樽漂白水/其他腐蝕性水<br />\n拿撚死垃圾防暴popo</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1bdeadef3bf4976867d557ad4226eeafec7b2f60","tid":1604080,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"［整合］十一執齊野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8fb75886fbed892318ab5caaeacc7646f2fe94d","tid":1604080,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"由be water，到Hit and run，到而家獅鳥召喚，最後原來都仲停留喺<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>走走走，見人走我就走</strong></span>，後面半gear同和理非嚇到雞飛狗走都唔知咩事，搞到走散哂，前線好易缺人，然後落單，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人多狗會淆，人少狗會咬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n不說走走走，試說急步行<br />\n不說跑呀衝緊埋黎，試說一二一二<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，三個月資訊都仲停留喺嗰邊有狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>邊度嗰邊！防暴便衣定速龍！數量！</strong></span><br />\n咁模糊嘅資訊好難叫大家部署，然後又係一味走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我要時地人一句過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不說嗰邊有狗，試說鵝頸橋五十防暴<br />\n不說呢邊有狗，試說海富橋四十速龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有明明手足同狗嘅比例係10：1甚至100：1<br />\n都係一味叫走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">都冇人召喚獅鳥冇人踢波<br />\n十月一號仲點樣賀佢老母呀，得把口</span></strong><br />\n特別係制高點！<br />\n灣仔：灣仔站天橋、狗總天橋<br />\n老銅：Sogo天橋、八爪魚橋<br />\n金鐘：正義道、紅棉道、海富天橋、夏愨<br />\n霸哂佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不說有狗走呀，試說有冇人踢波</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5909c0c95b806504819a0430e4595138754039b7","tid":1604080,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"十一博弈準備大全(象棋呀伯提供)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2635019d4426f5d421338f2afcfea6b8e83805f","tid":1604080,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7f41e76a1d07a6e003b1a5b394b351adb57907c","tid":1604080,"uid":290364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f604af50dad37f7a5cb6ebc456d833755a2592f2","tid":1604080,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"仲有講撚左好多次,萬一比狗捉撚住個書包,第一件事要好似火影跑咁鬆開個書包走左先<br />\n<br />\n當然啦,最好就書包向前啦,但有時阻住行動都無計<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要火影跑,唔好本能反能chok 手跑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"火影跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fa679bcafc87ffbc2dbf727e5eb9bb618fea39","tid":1604080,"uid":290364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:53:13.000Z","